                                Automatic dangerous animal detection with clear safety indicators. Ensure compliance with local regulations and safety requirements.
                            </p>
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="bg-primary-600 rounded-2xl py-16 px-6 sm:py-24 sm:px-12 lg:px-16">
